\c 10
\s Vanakomana vaJafeti, naHamu naShemu
\p
\v 1 Zvino iyi ndiyo rondedzero yemadzinza evanakomana vaNowa, Shemu, Hamu, naJafeti; ivo vakaberekerwa vanakomana shure kwemafashame.
\v 2 Vanakomana vaJafeti: Gomeri, naMagogi naMadhai naJavhani naTubhari naMisheki naTirasi.
\v 3 Nevanakomana vaGomeri: Ashikenazi naRifati naTogarima.
\v 4 Nevanakomana vaJavhani: Erisha naTarishisi, vaKitimi nevaDhodhanimu.
\v 5 Kubva kune ava zviwi izvi zvechirudzi zvakagoverwa munyika dzavo umwe neumwe nerurimi rwake, nemhuri dzavo, mundudzi dzavo.
\p
\v 6 Nevanakomana vaHamu: Kushi naMiziraimu naPuti naKenani.
\v 7 Uye vanakomana vaKushi: Sebha naHavhira naSabhita naRaama naSabhiteka. Nevanakomana vaRaama: Shebha naDhedhani.
\v 8 Kushi ndokubereka Nimurodhi, iye akatanga kuva une simba panyika.
\v 9 Iye waiva mudzimba une simba pamberi paJehovha; naizvozvo zvinonzi: SaNimurodhi, mudzimba une simba pamberi paJehovha.
\v 10 Uye mavambo eushe hwake aiva Bhabheri neEreki neAkadhi neKarine panyika yeShinari.
\v 11 Kwakabuda kunyika iyo Ashuri, ndokuvaka Ninivhe neRehobhoti-Ire neKara,
\v 12 neReseni pakati peNinivhe neKara, ndiro guta guru.
\v 13 Zvino Miziraimu akabereka vaRudhi nevaAnami nevaRehabhi nevaNafituhi,
\v 14 nevaPaturusi nevaKasiruhi (kwakabva ikoko vaFirisitia) nevaKafutori.
\p
\v 15 Zvino Kenani wakabereka Sidhoni, dangwe rake, naHeti,
\v 16 nemuJebhusi nemuAmori nemuGirigashi,
\v 17 nemuHivhi nemuAriki nemuSini,
\v 18 nemuArivhadhi nemuZemari nemuHamati. Zvino shure kweizvozvi mhuri dzemuKenani dzakapararira.
\v 19 Zvino muganhu wevaKenani wakabva paSidhoni ukaenda kuGerari kusvika kuGaza, uchienda kuSodhoma nekuGomora nekuAdhima neZibhoimu kusvika paRasha.
\v 20 Ava vanakomana vaHamu, nemhuri dzavo, nendimi dzavo, munyika dzavo, mundudzi dzavo.
\p
\v 21 NaShemu wakaberekerwa \add vana\add*; iyewo ndibaba vevana vese vaEbheru, mukoma waJafeti, mukuru.
\v 22 Vanakomana vaShemu: Eramu naAshuri naAripakishadhi naRudhi naAramu.
\v 23 Uye vanakomana vaAramu: Uzi naHuri naGeteri naMashi.
\v 24 Zvino Aripakishadhi wakabereka Shera, Shera ndokubereka Ebheri.
\v 25 Zvino kuna Ebheru kwakaberekerwa vanakomana vaviri: Zita reumwe raiva Peregi, nokuti pamazuva ake nyika yakakamurwa; uye zita remunin'ina wake raiva Jokitani.
\v 26 Jokitani ndokubereka Arimodhadhi naSherefi naHazarimavheti naJera,
\v 27 naHadhoramu naUzari naDhikira
\v 28 naObhari naAbhimaeri naShebha
\v 29 naOfiri naHavhira naJobhabhu; ava vese vaiva vanakomana vaJokitani.
\v 30 Neugaro hwavo hwaibva paMesha uchienda Sefari, gomo rekumabvazuva.
\v 31 Ava vanakomana vaShemu, nemhuri dzavo nendimi dzavo munyika dzavo, nendudzi dzavo.
\p
\v 32 Ava \add i\add*mhuri dzevanakomana vaNowa, nemazera avo nendudzi dzavo; kwavari kwakaparadzaniswa ndudzi panyika shure kwemafashame.
